org.cougaar.core.qos.metrics
Interface DataFeedRegistrationService

All Superinterfaces:
Service
All Known Implementing Classes:
NullMetricsServiceImpl, RSSMetricsServiceImpl
public interface DataFeedRegistrationService
extends Service

The primary function of this Service is to add new "data feeds" to the MetricsUpdateService. The concept of a data feed (ie, a raw data provider) is borrowed from the RSS; the precise semantics is left indeterminate at this level.
